room_title: Escape room "The Hunted" by Escape Mission Chattanooga in Chattanooga
room_description: While on a search for some missing hikers, you and your group come across an abandoned cabin in the woods. But you quickly realize that you are not alone, and an innocent break from the cold just put you in the hands of a rogue hunter that calls himself "The Revolutionary". He is responsible for the missing hikers and has captured them in his makeshift Room. Can you pull off the biggest rescue mission of your life and escape before you become his next target?
